GCDAsyncDownloadImage is a lightweight download & cache image tool, it's use GCD. It's simple but strong.

You can use GCDAsyncDownloadImage Or GCDImageView. I'am suggest you use GCDImageView.


引用方式:
 #import "GCDImageView.h"
 
 GCDImageView    *_imgView = [[GCDImageView alloc] initWithFrame:CGRectMake(...)];
 void (^failedCallBack)(void) = ^(void){NSLog(@"download image failed");};
 void (^successdCallBack)(void)  = ^(void){NSLog(@"download image success");};
 [_imgView getImageWithUrl:imgurl defaultImg:[UIImage imageNamed:@"default.png"] successBlock:successdCallBack failedBlock:failedCallBack];
 


